title: Wet Leg - Chaise Longue (Live at First Avenue in Minneapolis)
description:
Watch Wet Leg perform "Chaise Longue," recorded live at First Avenue in Minneapolis on Thursday, March 3, 2022.

Wet Leg's debut self-titled album released April 8, 2022, via Domino Recording Company. 

Band members:
Rhian Teasdale – vocals/guitar
Hester Chambers – guitar/vocals
Ellis-James Durant – bass
Joshua Mobaraki – keys/guitar
Henry Holmes – drums
